OL,3,CHead of Caldey Abbey apologises for
OL,4,C'great suffering' of abused children
OL,6,FThe review, led by former assistant
OL,7,Fpolice and crime commissioner at South
OL,8,FWales Police, Jan Pickles, examined
OL,9,Fallegations dating from the late 1960s
OL,10,Fto 1992. They had been made by people
OL,11,Fwho said they experienced abuse on the
OL,12,Fisland as children, some whom lived
OL,13,Fthere and others who visited.
