OL,3,CHead of Caldey Abbey apologises for
OL,4,C'great suffering' of abused children
OL,6,FCarl Harris, assistant director at
OL,7,FNSPCC Cymru, said: "It is deeply
OL,8,Ftroubling to read that child sexual
OL,9,Fabuse occurred 'in plain sight' on
OL,10,FCaldey Island and the voices of
OL,11,Fchildren were not heard.
OL,13,F"This independent review identifies
OL,14,Fclear missed opportunities to prevent
OL,15,Ffurther abuse and bring Kotik to
OL,16,Fjustice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
