OL,3,CHead of Caldey Abbey apologises for
OL,4,C'great suffering' of abused children
OL,6,F"It is particularly distressing to
OL,7,Fhear that children were not listened
OL,8,Fto and supported when they spoke up to
OL,9,Fraise concerns, and no action was
OL,10,Ftaken.
OL,12,F"The report further highlights the
OL,13,Fimportance of The Independent Inquiry
OL,14,Finto Child Sexual Abuse's (IICSA)
OL,15,Frecommendation on the need for
OL,16,Freligious organisations to have robust
OL,17,Fsafeguarding processes in place.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
