OL,3,CHead of Caldey Abbey apologises for
OL,4,C'great suffering' of abused children
OL,6,F"Child sexual abuse can have a
OL,7,Fdevastating effect on victims, which
OL,8,Fis why it is so important that
OL,9,Fsurvivors can be confident that if
OL,10,Fthey speak out they will be listened
OL,11,Fto and supported.
OL,13,F"We can all look out for children's
OL,14,Fwelfare, and anyone concerned about a
OL,15,Fchild can call the NSPCC Helpline on
OL,16,F0808 800 5000, or email
OL,17,Fhelp@nspcc.org.uk."
